title: Bandbox, 1825–30
description: a) Oval box covered with wallpaper. Foliate scrolls in lavender-blue with darker blue dots emphasizing the pattern in various places, on yellow ground. Margin visible at seam; b) Cover of the same as "a". Two joined sheets.

tombstone.epitaph:
Bandbox, 1825–30.
1825–30. Block-printed paper on pasteboard support. Gift of Mrs. Rollin Stickle. 1960-111-5-a,b.
